export default {
  name: "MainContent",
  data() {
    return{
      tableData: []

  methods: {
    loadGet() {
      this.$axios.get(this.$httpUrl+'/user/list').then(res => {
        console.log(res)
      })

    loadPost() {
      this.$axios.post(this.$httpUrl+'/user/listP',{}).then(res => {

        this.tableData=res.data
      })
    },

  beforeMount() {
    this.loadPost()
  }

}
